<body>
<nav><a href="/progrok/">Home</a><a href="/progrok/docs">Docs</a></nav>
<main>
<h1>Custom Voices</h1>
<p>Clone a voice by uploading audio samples via <code>POST /v1/custom-voices</code> with multipart form data. The cloned voice can then be used as a <code>voice_id</code> in TTS requests.</p>
<pre><code>{`curl -X POST http://localhost:18645/v1/custom-voices \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer $API_KEY" \
  -F "name=my-voice" \
  -F "samples=@sample1.mp3" \
  -F "samples=@sample2.mp3"`}</code></pre>
</main>
<footer style="margin-top:3rem;padding-top:1rem;border-top:1px solid #30363d;color:#8b949e;font-size:.85em">progrok — MIT License</footer>
</body>
</html>
